description:
Complete your look with this Ai Ai accessory! 
This accessory is a hat that Amigo can wear to dress up like Ai Ai from Super Monkey Ball.

This item is included in the Super Monkey Ball Costume & Accessories Pack.
Purchasing the Super Monkey Ball Costume & Accessories Pack will make this accessory available for your Amigo in the shop menu.
name: Ai Ai Accessory
